description:
This is a 10 minute workout called '10-Minute Meditation For Sleep' from the channel Goodful.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: If you are feeling restless, listen to this guided meditation to ease your mind and body into falling asleep. 

Written and Narrated by John Davisi. John is a mindfulness life coach, teacher, and speaker.
Check out all of his mindfulness and meditation sessions at https://www.johndavisi.com
